content: Robot reading the numbers doesn't help. Waste of money. It is a Microsoft Sam/woman voice.
replyContent: Thanks for your feedback. We use the voice built into your Android device to allow for every possible number to be included in this app. This makes the app more flexible, reasonably priced, and keeps it from taking up too much storage. We encourage all customers to try the free Lite version of the app before buying to avoid disappointment.
